@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About TradeScope AI";
}

<section class="about-hero">
    <h1>By traders, for traders.</h1>
    <p>TradeScope AI is the stock recommendation copilot that adapts to the trader behind the screen—whether you’re a swing tactician, day-trade scalper, or long-term accumulator with a specific risk tolerance.</p>
</section>

<section class="about-grid">
    <article>
        <h2>Signal Engine</h2>
        <p>We screen thousands of stocks against your trader type, playbooks like breakouts or quality compounding, and risk thresholds—fusing technical setups, fundamental trends, and outside-the-chart context to narrow the universe fast.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
        <h2>Explainable Intelligence</h2>
        <p>Each idea arrives with the “why now,” the signals behind it, entry and exit zones, plus risk parameters tuned to your tolerance. Ask for adjustments and the copilot explains options in trader-friendly language.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
        <h2>Human + Machine</h2>
        <p>Traders feed the AI real-world playbooks and edge cases, and the system keeps learning. The result: recommendations that respect how you manage trades while surfacing opportunities you might have missed.</p>
    </article>
</section>

